  "text": "Anti-CD25 antibody, applied intratumourally to target Treg within the tumour, resulted in 85% depletion of intratumoural Tregs and inhibited tumour growth, which was extended with multiple injections [CITATION_1] . These data suggest that removing Treg may contribute to the success of combination therapies.",
